<li><a href="/wiki/Cost_Per_Impression" title="Cost Per Impression" class="mw-redirect">CPI</a> - Cost Per Impression</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Pay_per_click" title="Pay per click">PPC</a> - Pay per click</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Cost_Per_Action" title="Cost Per Action" class="mw-redirect">CPA</a> - Cost Per Action or Acquisition</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Internet_marketing" title="Internet marketing">Internet marketing</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Cost_Per_Click" title="Cost Per Click" class="mw-redirect">CPC</a> - Cost Per Click</li>
